{"data":[{"date":"10:09 18/08","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Sanchez kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \"bom x\u1ecbt\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/26/nguoi-cu-mu-khang-dinh-sanchez-khong-phai-bom-xit.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Wes Brown kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Alexis Sanchez v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u201cbom x\u1ecbt\u201d c\u1ee7a Man United.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Man United \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng si\u00eau sao Alexis Sanchez t\u1eeb Arsenal \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Chile ch\u01b0a thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Old Trafford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSanchez kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man United. Anh ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n sau 18 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi trong h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Alexis Sanchez kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i bom x\u1ecbt h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Alexis Sanchez kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i bom x\u1ecbt h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/Nguoi-cu-MU-khang-dinh-Alexis-Sanchez-khong-phai-bom-xit-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Wes Brown kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Alexis Sanchez kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \"bom x\u1ecbt\" c\u1ee7a MU</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng Wes Brown tin r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Sanchez s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng minh \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Daily Star, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 MU cho bi\u1ebft: <em>\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c MU mua Sanchez l\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 sai l\u1ea7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Sanchez l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf Arsenal. Ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00f2a nh\u1eadp. V\u00e0 sau 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00fang v\u1ec1 Sanchez. Ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 t\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n theo th\u1eddi gian\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nS\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Sanchez trong th\u00e1ng M\u1ed9t \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c \u1edf Man United. Martial l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ecb \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t v\u00ec m\u1ea5t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn tin \u0111\u1ed3n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111ang t\u00ecm b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i th\u00edch Martial. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y l\u00e0 m\u1eabu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 lu\u00f4n \u0111e d\u1ecda \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cMartial l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00e0 ch\u1ed7 c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ea5u \u00e1c li\u1ec7t. Man United \u0111ang c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-dang-le-phai-lam-doi-truong-man-utd-tu-luc-moi-ve-172-194712.html\">Pogba \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Man Utd t\u1eeb l\u00fac m\u1edbi v\u1ec1</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/huyen-thoai-mu-doi-ban-quach-pogba-di-vi-thai-do-172-194664.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU \u0111\u00f2i b\u00e1n qu\u00e1ch Pogba \u0111i v\u00ec th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2498","checkdouble":"194719"},{"date":"10:20 18/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 th\u00f3i l\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Ozil","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/huyen-thoai-bao-ve-thoi-luoi-phong-ngu-cua-ozil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Kanu cho r\u1eb1ng Arsenal c\u1ea7n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a Ozil ho\u1eb7c l\u00e0 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Ozil \u0111ang b\u1ecb s\u0103m soi k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng sau v\u1ee5 l\u00f9m x\u00f9m khi\u1ebfn anh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c. Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Arsenal, Ozil b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u1eefng c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1. Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 29 tu\u1ed5i ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng kh\u00f4ng n\u0103ng n\u1ed5 v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng t\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u1eabu v\u1eady, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Kanu \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Ozil. Anh cho r\u1eb1ng Arsenal n\u00ean t\u1eadp trung ph\u00e1t huy s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Ozil thay v\u00ec b\u1eaft c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kanu b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Ozil tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec th\u00f3i l\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kanu b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Ozil tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch v\u00ec th\u00f3i l\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/huyen-thoai-bao-ve-thoi-luoi-phong-ngu-cua-ozil.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Kanu b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 Ozil tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00e1c nhau. \u0110i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a Ozil ch\u1ee9 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a c\u1eadu \u1ea5y. Ozil c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn th\u00ec b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ra \u0111i. Ban kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n Maradona hay Messi ph\u1ea3i lui v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1. B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecd t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd bi\u1ebft l\u00e0m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00ec HLV ph\u1ea3i l\u1ef1a theo n\u00f3 v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Ozil ph\u00e1t huy s\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft t\u1ea1i sao m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eabn ph\u00e0n n\u00e0n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 Ozil l\u00e0 thi tho\u1ea3ng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t thi\u1ebfu t\u1eadp trung. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng bao gi\u1edd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nOzil v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c mang t\u00ean Chelsea. \u1ede tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n g\u1eb7p Man City, Ozil \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t v\u00e0 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n cho Arsenal. Anh thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 v\u1eadt v\u1edd m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Emery \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 h\u1ea1t nh\u00e2n quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nhan-dinh-chelsea-vs-arsenal-23h30-ngay-188-dung-lay-man-city-lam-thuoc-do-172-194717.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Chelsea vs Arsenal (23h30 ng\u00e0y 18/8): \u0110\u1eebng l\u1ea5y Man City l\u00e0m th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-arsenal-da-deu-thay-cu-wenger-khong-biet-huan-luyen-172-194710.html\">Sao Arsenal \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ec3u th\u1ea7y c\u0169 Wenger kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2497","checkdouble":"194723"},{"date":"10:21 18/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Barca vs Alaves (3h15 ng\u00e0y 19/8): Cu\u1ed9c \u0111ua b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-barca-vs-alaves-3h15-ngay-198-cuoc-dua-bat-dau.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Rennes vs Angers l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Ph\u00e1p Ligue 1 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Rennes vs Angers 01h00 ng\u00e0y 198 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Rennes vs Angers 01h00 ng\u00e0y 198 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/Rennes_vs_Angers.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Rennes vs Angers</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Rennes vs Angers: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Angers ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt m\u1edbi tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c an ph\u1eadn m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00f9a chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n7 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 n\u00e0y Angers kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Ligue 1 2018/19, Angers d\u00f9 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng Nimes.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, Rennes \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 Europa League. Kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Rennes b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017-2018. S\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng trong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i gi\u00fap Rennes kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Rennes ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau duy tr\u00ec th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng trong top 5. Do v\u1eady, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Angers.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nRennes: T. Koubek, Mexer, I. Sarr, C. Grenier, J. Lea Siliki, B. Bourigeaud, B. Andr\u00e9, Ludovic Baal, D. Sakho, J. Gelin, H. Traor\u00e9.<br>\r\nAngers: L. Butelle, T. Mangani, V. Pajot, I. Traor\u00e9, A. Fulgini, P. Capelle, S. Bahoken, F. Tait, R. Thomas, A. Bamba, V. Manceau.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2496","checkdouble":"194724"},{"date":"11:04 18/08","title":"\"Pochettino s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/pochettino-se-khong-tu-choi-neu-duoc-moi-dan-dat-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Jermain Jenas cho r\u1eb1ng HLV Pochettino s\u1ebd r\u1eddi Tottenham \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Man United n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Pochettino \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi sau khi \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1ea1i Premier League. \u00d4ng \u0111\u00e3 bi\u1ebfn Tottenham tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean cho m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trong top 4 Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn Pochettino t\u1eebng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c li\u00ean h\u1ec7 d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Real thay cho Zidane. Nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Pochettino s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Pochettino s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1eddi d\u1eabn d\u1eaft MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/pochettino-se-khong-tu-choi-neu-duoc-moi-dan-dat-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>HLV\u00a0Pochettino kh\u00e1 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Man United</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nJermain Jenas tin r\u1eb1ng Los Blancos c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00f4i k\u00e9o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Pochettino n\u1ebfu g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Spurs c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Pochettino kh\u00f3 c\u01b0\u1ee1ng l\u1ea1i l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb Man United n\u1ebfu Mourinho ra \u0111i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u0111\u00e3 theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Pochettino \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian. \u0110\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec1u l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u1eed th\u00e1ch l\u1edbn. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Pochettino r\u1ea5t th\u00edch nh\u1eefng c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c th\u1eed th\u00e1ch nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Man United v\u00e0 Real Madrid m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a Pochettino.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cJurgen Klopp s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111i \u0111\u00e2u ngo\u00e0i Liverpool. Chelsea thay \u0111\u1ed5i HLV h\u00e0ng n\u0103m. N\u1ebfu \u00f4ng \u1ea5y d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea th\u00ec m\u1ecdi c\u00f4ng s\u1ee9c x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng \u1edf Spurs coi nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed5 s\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ed5 b\u1ec3 h\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cPochettino c\u0169ng t\u1eebng n\u00f3i r\u1eb1ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ebfn Barcelona v\u00ec c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t cho Espanyol. V\u00ec v\u1eady, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn d\u00e0nh cho Pochettino. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Bayern, PSG v\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng \u00f4ng \u1ea5y s\u1ebd mu\u1ed1n \u1edf l\u1ea1i Premier League ho\u1eb7c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i La Liga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cN\u1ebfu Mourinho r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi Man United, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu h\u1ecd theo \u0111u\u1ed5i Pochettino quy\u1ebft li\u1ec7t. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra \u1edf Spurs, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u1edf l\u1ea1i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 MU:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/nguoi-cu-mu-khang-dinh-sanchez-khong-phai-bom-xit-172-194719.html\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Sanchez kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i bom x\u1ecbt</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/pogba-dang-le-phai-lam-doi-truong-man-utd-tu-luc-moi-ve-172-194712.html\">Pogba \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Man Utd t\u1eeb l\u00fac m\u1edbi v\u1ec1</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2495","checkdouble":"194725"},{"date":"10:47 18/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Amiens vs Montpellier 01h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (Ligue 1 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/104333-Amiens-vs-Montpellier.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Amiens vs Montpellier l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Ph\u00e1p Ligue 1 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Amiens vs Montpellier\" title=\"Amiens vs Montpellier\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/104333-Amiens-vs-Montpellier.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Amiens vs Montpellier</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\nNh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Amiens vs Montpellier: 2-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Montpellier tr\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea7y t\u1ef1 tin b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 nh\u1edd qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu r\u1ea5t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng (4 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 2 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng). BL\u0110 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169ng c\u00f3 c\u00e1c th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1 kh\u00f4n ngoan \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Ga\u00ebtan Laborde, Florent Mollet hay Junior Sambia.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, ngay tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Ligue 1 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p Dijon ngay t\u1ea1i th\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ecba c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. N\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng giai \u0111o\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Montpellier lu\u00f4n ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n nh\u00e0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean kia chi\u1ebfn tuy\u1ebfn, Amiens c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t khi nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf chuy\u1ebfn l\u00e0m kh\u00e1ch t\u1edbi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Lyon trong tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, th\u1ef1c l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Amiens kh\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, c\u1ed9ng th\u00eam vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch n\u00ean th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u00f2ng 2 n\u00e0y, Amiens \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, n\u01a1i h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00e1 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi chu\u1ed7i 5 tr\u1eadn li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i (3 th\u1eafng), trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a c\u1ea3 \u00f4ng l\u1edbn PSG 2-2. 6 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Montpellier tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Amiens c\u0169ng b\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi 4 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a.</div>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2494","checkdouble":"194726"},{"date":"10:58 18/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Rennes vs Angers 01h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (Ligue 1 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-rennes-vs-angers-01h00-ngay-198-ligue-1-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Rennes vs Angers l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Ph\u00e1p Ligue 1 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Rennes vs Angers 01h00 ng\u00e0y 198 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Rennes vs Angers 01h00 ng\u00e0y 198 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/Rennes_vs_Angers.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Rennes vs Angers</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> Rennes vs Angers: 2-0<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Angers ph\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt m\u1edbi tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ebfn m\u00f9a n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c an ph\u1eadn m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng. H\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng trong m\u00f9a chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n7 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 n\u00e0y Angers kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ebfm tr\u1ea3i c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn m\u1edf m\u00e0n Ligue 1 2018/19, Angers d\u00f9 c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba l\u00ean h\u1ea1ng Nimes.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0, Rennes \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc gi\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t d\u1ef1 Europa League. Kh\u00f4ng nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u00e0nh t\u00edch n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a Rennes b\u1edfi h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn su\u1ed1t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017-2018. S\u1ef1 \u0111a d\u1ea1ng trong c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i gi\u00fap Rennes kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a n\u00e0y, Rennes ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau duy tr\u00ec th\u1ee9 h\u1ea1ng trong top 5. Do v\u1eady, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 nh\u01b0 Angers.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nRennes: T. Koubek, Mexer, I. Sarr, C. Grenier, J. Lea Siliki, B. Bourigeaud, B. Andr\u00e9, Ludovic Baal, D. Sakho, J. Gelin, H. Traor\u00e9.<br>\r\nAngers: L. Butelle, T. Mangani, V. Pajot, I. Traor\u00e9, A. Fulgini, P. Capelle, S. Bahoken, F. Tait, R. Thomas, A. Bamba, V. Manceau.</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2493","checkdouble":"194727"},{"date":"11:04 18/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Caen vs Nice 01h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (Ligue 1 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-caen-vs-nice-01h00-ngay-198-ligue-1-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Caen vs Nice l\u00fac 01h00 ng\u00e0y 19/8 (V\u00f2ng 2 gi\u1ea3i V\u0110QG Ph\u00e1p Ligue 1 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia, d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, ph\u00e2n t\u00edch chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n, c\u00e1c th\u00f4ng tin t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea b\u00ean l\u1ec1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</h2><div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Caen vs Nice 01h00 ng\u00e0y 198 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Caen vs Nice 01h00 ng\u00e0y 198 Ligue 1 201819 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/18/Nhan-dinh-caen-vs-nice.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Caen vs Nice</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Caen vs Nice: 2-1<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\n<div>Nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n Ligue 1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19 tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 PSG tr\u00ean s\u00e2n kh\u00e1ch c\u00f3 l\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec7n g\u00ec \u0111\u00e1ng bu\u1ed3n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Caen. B\u1edfi \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc, khi m\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ch\u00eanh l\u1ec7ch gi\u1eefa \u0111\u00f4i b\u00ean l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Caen c\u0169ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u00e0 cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i r\u1ea5t t\u1ec7 khi ch\u1ec9 th\u1eafng 1/4 giao h\u1eefu. H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 m\u01a1 ng\u1ee7 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn chu\u1ed7i th\u00e0nh t\u00edch ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n c\u1ee7a Caen.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u00ean ph\u1ea7n s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n, Nice \u0111\u00e3 chia tay HLV Lucien Favre, ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 tr\u01b0\u1edfng trong th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u1edf 2 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 3 chung cu\u1ed9c \u1edf m\u00f9a 2016/17. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n gh\u1ebf n\u00f3ng l\u00e0 huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Arsenal v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ph\u00e1p, Patrick Vieira. Tuy nhi\u00ean, d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNice c\u0169ng \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n b\u1ed9 m\u1eb7t t\u1ec7 kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m Caen.\u00a0H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 h\u00f4ng th\u1eafng 4 tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i trong tr\u1eadn m\u1edf \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i Ligue 1 2018/19 ngay tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng y\u1ebfu h\u01a1n Brest. Xem ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 Nice c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec3m r\u1eddi s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a Caen l\u00e0 b\u1ea5t kh\u1ea3 thi.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2492","checkdouble":"194728"},{"date":"11:14 18/08","title":"N