lautern vs Hoffenheim</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\">\r\n<h2 style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/nhan-dinh-bong-da-c344-p1.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1</span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> </span></span></span></span></span></span></span>Kaiserslautern vs Hoffenheim: 0-3<br>\r\n</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></h2>\r\nKhi Kaiserslautern l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 4 trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111o\u1ea1t ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Bundesliga v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 5/1998, Hoffenheim v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng 5 \u0110\u1ee9c. \u1ea4y v\u1eady m\u00e0, sau 2 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7, v\u1ecb th\u1ebf hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea3o ng\u01b0\u1ee3c. Trong khi Hoffenheim s\u1eafp s\u1eeda b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i th\u1ee9 11 t\u1ea1i Bundesliga, th\u00ec Kaiserslautern \u0111ang ng\u1ee5p l\u1eb7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i h\u1ea1ng 3. <br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc Kaiserslautern c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Bundesliga 2 nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u00ean BXH \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 bi\u1ec7t danh The Red Devils ph\u1ea3i xu\u1ed1ng h\u1ea1ng T\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y, Kaiserslautern \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 4 tr\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00f4ng kh\u1ea3 quan.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u00f3 ph\u1ea7n may m\u1eafn \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1, h\u1ecd thu v\u1ec1 v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1/9 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1i \u0111a \u1edf 3 v\u00f2ng ti\u1ebfp theo. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111ang th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n, Kaiserslautern kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i nay \u1edf c\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u01a1i tr\u00ean s\u00e2n nh\u00e0<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn:<br>\r\nKaiserslautern: Sievers; Dick, Kraus, Sternberg, \u00d6zdemir, Albaek, Hemlein, Pick, Fechner, Thiele, Spalvis.<br>\r\nHoffenheim: Baumann; Adams, Vogt, Bicakcic, Kaderabek, Demirbay, Schulz, Amiri, Grifo, Joelinton, Szalai.</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"2491","checkdouble":"194729"},{"date":"11:23 18/08","title":"Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Drochtersen vs Bayern Munich 20h30 ng\u00e0y 18/8 (C\u00fap QG \u0110\u1ee9c 2018/19)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/18/nhan-dinh-drochtersen-vs-bayern-munich-20h30-ngay-188-cup-qg-duc-201819.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Drochtersen vs Bayern Munich l\u00fac 20h30 ng\u00e0y 18/8 (C\u00fap qu\u1ed1c gia \u0110\u1ee9c 2018/19): Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u00fd ki\u1ebfn chuy\u00ean gia